OL,3,CRAF scrambles jets after unidentified
OL,4,Caircraft approached British airspace
OL,6,FThe RAF scrambled two fighter jets on
OL,7,FTuesday after sightings of an
OL,8,Funidentified aircraft approaching
OL,9,FBritish airspace.
OL,11,FThe jets, which were launched from RAF
OL,12,FLossiemouth in north Scotland, were
OL,13,Fsupported by a Voyager refuelling jet
OL,14,Ffrom RAF Brize Norton in Oxfordshire.
OL,16,FAn RAF spokesperson told ITV News:
OL,17,F"RAF Quick Reaction Alert Typhoon
OL,18,Ffighter aircraft were launched on
OL,19,FApril 14 from RAF Lossiemouth after
OL,20,Funidentified aircraft were tracked
OL,21,Fflying towards UK airspace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
