FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776255071
OL,3,CRAF scrambles jets after unidentified
OL,4,Caircraft approached British airspace
OL,6,F"The unidentified aircraft remained
OL,7,Foutside of our area of interest, and
OL,8,Fno intercepts took place."
OL,10,FThe Telegraph reported that the
OL,11,Funidentified aircraft was a suspected
OL,12,FRussian long-range bomber.
OL,14,FIt comes as officials have raised
OL,15,Fconcerns about Russian naval movements
OL,16,Fin the last year.
OL,18,FIn 2020, two Russian Bear-F Tu-142
OL,19,Flong-range aircraft were intercepted
OL,20,Fby the RAF as they flew towards
OL,21,FBritain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
