PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776255071
OL,3,CRAF scrambles jets after unidentified
OL,4,Caircraft approached British airspace
OL,6,FLast week, Defence Secretary John
OL,7,FHealey announced the UK military had
OL,8,Fobserved a Russian attack submarine
OL,9,Fand two spy submarines in the North
OL,10,FAtlantic for a month before they
OL,11,Fretreated.
OL,13,FHe said this came at a period of
OL,14,F"increased Russian activity", with
OL,15,FVladimir Putin hoping to capitalise
OL,16,Fwhile the world was distracted by war
OL,17,Fin Iran and Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
