PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776255071
OL,3,CRAF scrambles jets after unidentified
OL,4,Caircraft approached British airspace
OL,6,FThis operation involved a Russian
OL,7,FAkula-class nuclear-powered attack
OL,8,Fsubmarine and two specialist
OL,9,Fsubmarines from Russia's Ministry of
OL,10,FDefence deep-sea research programme
OL,11,Fknown as Gugi (Main Directorate of
OL,12,FDeep-Sea Research), he said.
OL,14,FHealey described Putin as "the primary
OL,15,Fthreat to UK security".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
