OL,3,CRAF scrambles jets after unidentified
OL,4,Caircraft approached British airspace
OL,6,FAddressing him directly, he said: "We
OL,7,Fsee your activity over our cables and
OL,8,Four pipelines, and you should know
OL,9,Fthat any attempt to damage them will
OL,10,Fnot be tolerated and will have serious
OL,11,Fconsequences."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe defence secretary is set to speak
OL,19,Fin Berlin on Wednesday afternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
