OL,3,CRAF scrambles jets after unidentified
OL,4,Caircraft approached British airspace
OL,6,FWhile there, he will to co-chair a
OL,7,Fmeeting of the 50-nation Ukraine
OL,8,FDefence Contact Group alongside Nato
OL,9,FSecretary General Mark Rutte, and the
OL,10,FUkrainian and German defence ministers.
OL,12,FHis appearance in Berlin comes as the
OL,13,FUK announces a shipment of 120,000
OL,14,Fdrones to aid Ukraine's war effort -
OL,15,Fthe largest delivery of its kind,
OL,16,Faccording to the MoD.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
